(82, 1, '2020-06-27 05:53:51', '2020-06-27 05:53:51', 'Stay cozy and comfortable all year long, even in the toughest Canadian winter. The LG Art Cool Prestige provides powerful cooling and heating with high efficiency. Its Inverter Compressor automatically adjusts speed to maintain your desired temperature levels. Plus, you can control it anytime, from anywhere, using your smartphone.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>LG ThinQ controls your ductless heat pump anywhere with a Wi-Fi equipped device</li>\r\n 	<li>Energy-saving Inverter Compressor constantly adjusts to the right temperature</li>\r\n 	<li>Operates at low sound levels with LG’s unique skew fan and DUAL Inverter Compressor™</li>\r\n 	<li>Stylish design that will fit in your room interior design and lighten your room.</li>\r\n 	<li>Saves energy, perfect solution for additional heating source</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAvailable in multiple BTUs.', 'LG Heat Pump', 'Low monthly payments', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lg-heat-pump', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:26:18', '2021-03-31 15:26:18', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=82', 0, 'products', '', 0),
