(219, 1, '2020-07-15 04:16:24', '2020-07-15 04:16:24', 'My family and I just had a water filter and air filter installed in our home. We noticed the difference right away. The taste of the water and freshness of the air were obvious to my 4-year-old.\r\n\r\nI know this sounds cliché, but I never thought I needed these products, but now I wonder how I ever lived without them. Thanks Simply Green for your help.', 'Timothy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'timothy', '', '', '2020-08-14 16:52:18', '2020-08-14 16:52:18', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=testimonials&#038;p=219', 0, 'testimonials', '', 0),
