(222, 1, '2020-07-15 04:18:18', '2020-07-15 04:18:18', 'We were approached at the doors from a rep (Rob Kish) who had lots of information that helped us make a decision to have a furnace and hot water tank installed. We felt that Simply Green did an excellent job.\r\n\r\nWe would be honoured to pass your name around to family and friends. Awesome job guys. Thanks for everything.', 'Eva Jane', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'eva-jane', '', '', '2020-07-15 04:18:18', '2020-07-15 04:18:18', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=testimonials&#038;p=222', 0, 'testimonials', '', 0),
