(316, 1, '2020-07-17 04:43:15', '2020-07-17 04:43:15', 'Designed to provide many years of cooling comfort, the Goodman 13 SEER is an affordable, reliable and energy-efficient system. It offers up to 14 SEER cooling performance, which adds up to lower energy bills compared to lower-rated SEER compressors.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Single-Speed Condenser Fan Motor provides dependable, quiet airflow</li>\r\n 	<li>Factory-installed filter drier absorbs and filters residual system contaminants and moisture</li>\r\n 	<li>Fully charged for fifteen feet of tubing length</li>\r\n 	<li>Meets performance requirements for AHRI certification and complies with ETL North American safety standards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAvailable in multiple SEERs', 'Goodman Air Conditioner', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'goodman-13-seer-air-conditioner', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:23:48', '2021-03-31 15:23:48', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=316', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(317, 1, '2020-07-17 04:44:36', '2020-07-17 04:44:36', 'Instead of sweating it out during the warm months, stay cool with the Keeprite Performance, a budget-friendly central air conditioner with that uses a single-stage compressor that’s compatible with most cooling thermostats.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Quiet performance (as low as 71 decibels)*</li>\r\n 	<li>Durably built to withstand bad weather and debris</li>\r\n 	<li>Designed for corrosion resistance and lasting performance</li>\r\n 	<li>Non-ozone depleting R-410A refrigerant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAvailable in multiple SEERs', 'KeepRite Air Conditioner', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'keeprite-13-seer-air-conditioner', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:22:19', '2021-03-31 15:22:19', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=317', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(318, 1, '2020-07-17 04:45:44', '2020-07-17 04:45:44', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Alternative to conventional AC</li>\r\n 	<li>Can be placed anywhere in your home</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintains perfect temperature throughout the year</li>\r\n 	<li>Uses up to 70% less energy</li>\r\n 	<li>Automatic error-monitoring system</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Samsung Smart Whisper Ductless Air Conditioner', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'samsung-smart-whisper-ductless-air-conditioner', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:21:42', '2021-03-31 15:21:42', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=318', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(319, 1, '2020-07-17 04:46:50', '2020-07-17 04:46:50', 'Did you know that improving humidity in your home can actually make it feel warmer indoors? The Honeywell Humidifier’s PerfectFLO system optimizes water usage to reduce costs and mounts easily on either the warm air supply or return air duct of forced-air furnaces.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Flow-through design keeps the unit clean of microorganisms</li>\r\n 	<li>Properly humidified air protects wood floors and furnishings</li>\r\n 	<li>Evaporator pad helps filter out minerals from hard water and other impurities</li>\r\n 	<li>Less maintenance and cleaning than portable units</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Honeywell Humidifier', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'honeywell-humidifier', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:21:14', '2021-03-31 15:21:14', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=319', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(320, 1, '2020-07-17 04:48:03', '2020-07-17 04:48:03', 'Indoor pollution levels can be 25 times and occasionally 100 times more polluted than outdoor air, according to the EPA. A High-Efficiency Media or Electronic Air Cleaner is not enough to filter the millions of pollutants generated and infiltrating our homes daily. A HEPA Air Cleaner combined with an Electronic or Media Air Cleaner will provide much finer air filtration.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ideal for allergy, asthma, or respiratory sufferers</li>\r\n 	<li>Reduces housekeeping time</li>\r\n 	<li>Protects renovators and new homeowners from excessive dust and odors off-gassed from new carpets, construction materials, paints, and more</li>\r\n 	<li>Makes a noticeable difference for households with pets, offensive cooking odors, and mustiness</li>\r\n</ul>', 'HEPA Filtration', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hepa-filtration', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:20:41', '2021-03-31 15:20:41', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=320', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(321, 1, '2020-07-17 04:49:15', '2020-07-17 04:49:15', 'A Heat Recovery Ventilator RV (HRV) circulates air throughout a home, drawing in air from outside and expelling indoor air out. All air that moves through an HRV passes through a heat-exchange core, which regulates the temperature of the air that the HRV releases into the home and sends back outside.\r\n\r\nLifeBreath 155 Max Residential HRV:\r\nMove air more efficiently through your home and lower your heating bills. The LifeBreath 155 Max features a High-Efficiency Hex Core to ensure maximum heat transfer, low-pressure loss, constructed of thermally conductive and durable aluminum.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Door Port Balancing &amp; adjustable dampers</li>\r\n 	<li>Excellent low-temperature performance</li>\r\n 	<li>Controller with 5-speed, 4-mode operation, included</li>\r\n 	<li>Latched door to allow easy access to core and filters for cleaning. 25\" clearance recommended</li>\r\n</ul>', 'HRV', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hrv', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:20:11', '2021-03-31 15:20:11', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=321', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(322, 1, '2020-07-17 04:50:34', '2020-07-17 04:50:34', 'Saving energy doesn’t mean inconvenience. The Navien Tankless Water Heater has a built-in insulated buffer tank and recirculation pump to eliminate the \"cold water sandwich\" effect and issues of minimum flow rates commonly found in other tankless water heaters.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dual stainless steel heat exchangers resist corrosion better than copper to provide longer life.</li>\r\n 	<li>Wifi connectivity - Wi-Fi enabled with NaviLink® add-on</li>\r\n 	<li>User-friendly control panel offers multiple features, including self-diagnostics</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Navien Tankless Water Heater', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'navien-tankless-water-heater', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:19:33', '2021-03-31 15:19:33', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=322', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(323, 1, '2020-07-17 04:51:46', '2020-07-17 04:51:46', 'Enjoy an endless supply of hot water on demand with the SENSEI™ RU160iN Super High-Efficiency Plus. It’s unobtrusive, too: the whole system is only the size of a small suitcase.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Runs on natural gas, easy-to-install and maintain and for indoor locations</li>\r\n 	<li>Qualified with an Energy Factor of 0.95 / Uniform Energy Factor of 0.93</li>\r\n 	<li>15,000 BTU (Minimum) / 160,000 BTU (Maximum)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Rinnai Tankless Water Heater', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rinnai-tankless-water-heater', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:19:01', '2021-03-31 15:19:01', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=323', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(324, 1, '2020-07-17 04:52:50', '2020-07-17 04:52:50', 'The Navien NCB-E is the first high efficiency condensing combination boiler with the capacity to supply both heat and domestic hot water for larger homes — enough hydronic heat for a whole house, plus hot water to run two showers and a dishwasher all at the same time.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Takes up 80% less space than a traditional floor standing boiler and storage tank</li>\r\n 	<li>Wi-Fi enabled with NaviLink® add-on</li>\r\n 	<li>Built-in insulated buffer tank and recirculation pump to eliminate the \"cold water sandwich\" effect and issues of minimum flow rates commonly found in other tankless water heaters.</li>\r\n 	<li>Super condensing efficiency</li>\r\n 	<li>Dual stainless steel heat exchangers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAvailable in multiple BTUs', 'Navien Water Boiler', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'navien-water-boiler', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:17:38', '2021-03-31 15:17:38', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=324', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(325, 1, '2020-07-17 04:56:39', '2020-07-17 04:56:39', 'Reverse osmosis systems offer one of the best ways of producing clean water for your household. Unlike other water filtering solutions, these systems are very efficient and capable of removing up to 95 to 99% of the contaminants in your water.\r\n\r\nExcalibur Superior Model 5 Stage Reverse Osmosis System:\r\nEnjoy pure water drinking water the way nature intended it. With the Excalibur 5 Stage Reverse Osmosis system, you’ll enjoy pure refreshing water, crystal clear ice cubes, and better-tasting coffee, tea and fruit drinks.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>75 Gallons per day capacity</li>\r\n 	<li>5 micron Polypropylene spun filtration for silt, dirt, rust, turbidity and iron removal</li>\r\n 	<li>10 micron Carbon Block Filtration to eliminate chlorine, THM’s and taste and odour</li>\r\n 	<li>5 micron Carbon Block Filtration to remove volatile, industrial chemicals</li>\r\n 	<li>Can be connected to refrigerator for water and ice</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Reverse Osmosis', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'reverse-osmosis', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:16:53', '2021-03-31 15:16:53', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=325', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(326, 1, '2020-07-17 04:57:43', '2020-07-17 04:57:43', 'Hard water leaves your hair and skin scaly and dry. It also makes your clothes dingy and increases energy and water-heating costs. Water Softeners provide top-of-the-line protection against the many problems that hard water poses to a household.\r\n\r\nNovosoft 485HE Series Water Softener:\r\nUse up to 75% less salt and up to 64% less water with this premier high-efficiency softener. You’ll enjoy softer, better water, and it’s easier and faster to install than ever.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Reverse Flow Regeneration preserves an unused portion of softening bed from unnecessary exchange saving salt</li>\r\n 	<li>Precision Brining calculates the exact amount of brine required to regenerate</li>\r\n 	<li>Soft Water Brine Tank Refill keeps tank &amp; injectors clean</li>\r\n 	<li>User-friendly backlit LCD display</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Water Softener', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'water-softener', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:16:01', '2021-03-31 15:16:01', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=326', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(327, 1, '2020-07-17 04:58:50', '2020-07-17 04:58:50', 'Rid your water of hardness &amp; bad tastes and odour caused by chlorine, chloramines, or organic matter. A full water treatment system gives you the best protection and best-tasting water.\r\n\r\nNovosoft 485 HTO:\r\nGet fresher water – and keep it fresh. This unique two-tank system keeps the two media beds separate and allows for more carbon contact improving chlorine, chloramines, and organic removal. Plus, the two tanks make replacing key filters easier.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dedicated softening &amp; carbon filtration tanks provide truly refined water</li>\r\n 	<li>NSF Certified control valve with electronic sensors, adjustable cycles &amp; proven piston, seal &amp; spacer design</li>\r\n 	<li>Automatic system refresh flushes stagnant water</li>\r\n 	<li>User-friendly backlit LCD display</li>\r\n 	<li>48-hour self-charging battery back-up</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Water Treatment System', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'water-treatment-systems', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:15:25', '2021-03-31 15:15:25', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=327', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(328, 1, '2020-07-17 05:00:12', '2020-07-17 05:00:12', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Instant Informational Alerts.</li>\r\n 	<li>Self-cleaning valve offers maximum performance and long life.</li>\r\n 	<li>Powerful, self-lubricating 75-inch-per-pound drive motor.</li>\r\n 	<li>EC5 uses less electricity than conventional AC power supplies found on other brands of water treatment equipment.</li>\r\n 	<li>Proportional Brine and Rinse.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'EC5 Water Conditioning System', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ec5-water-conditioning-system', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:14:56', '2021-03-31 15:14:56', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=328', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(329, 1, '2020-07-17 05:01:09', '2020-07-17 05:01:09', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Membrane cartridge filters on a molecular level to reduce unwanted minerals like chromium, copper and lead.</li>\r\n 	<li>Carbon block sediment pre-filter reduces chlorine levels and removes particles as small as 10 microns in size from your drinking water.</li>\r\n 	<li>Carbon block sediment post-filter reduces harmful Volatile Organic Compounds (VOC’s) that are dangerous to human health and the environment.</li>\r\n 	<li>NSF certified.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Ultrefiner II', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ultrefiner-ii', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:14:12', '2021-03-31 15:14:12', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=329', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(330, 1, '2020-07-17 05:02:05', '2020-07-17 05:02:05', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Downflow Model Filters out sediment as well as removing unwanted tastes and odors</li>\r\n 	<li>Tested and Certified by independent experts to ensure the effective reduction of chlorine and 50 volatile organic compounds (VOCs)</li>\r\n 	<li>Two filter options - Homeowners can choose between HYSULEX™ and SUPER HYSULEX™ activated carbon, both of which are manufactured to be cleaner, stronger, and harder than industry standard carbons</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Whole Home Carbon Filtration System', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'whole-house-carbon-filtration-system', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:13:23', '2021-03-31 15:13:23', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=330', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(331, 1, '2020-07-17 05:03:15', '2020-07-17 05:03:15', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Immediate Condition Response – by pushing any button, check the system status for notifications.</li>\r\n 	<li>3 alarm tones — low salt, no salt, and when service is required.</li>\r\n 	<li>Proportional Brine and Rinse.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'EC4 OxyTech', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ec4-oxytech', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:41:15', '2021-03-31 15:41:15', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=331', 0, 'products', '', 0),
(332, 1, '2020-07-17 05:04:23', '2020-07-17 05:04:23', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Detergent savings - Saves money by reducing or even eliminating usage of laundry detergent.</li>\r\n 	<li>Energy savings – no warm or hot water required.</li>\r\n 	<li>Environmentally responsible - By eliminating hot water and detergents, you will be using less energy and no longer dumping thousands of gallons of soaps and toxic bleach into the environment.</li>\r\n 	<li>No chemical irritation - eradicate common skin irritation caused by harsh cleaning detergents and disinfection products.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'CleanStart', 'Ideal for a 2,500 sq. ft. home', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cleanstart-2', '', '', '2021-03-31 15:40:25', '2021-03-31 15:40:25', '', 0, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/?post_type=products&#038;p=332', 0, 'products', '', 0),
