(647, 2, '2020-10-19 21:12:01', '2020-10-19 21:12:01', 'Stay cozy and comfortable all year long, even in the toughest Canadian winter. The LG Art Cool Prestige provides powerful cooling and heating with high efficiency. Its Inverter Compressor automatically adjusts speed to maintain your desired temperature levels. Plus, you can control it anytime, from anywhere, using your smartphone.\n<ul>\n 	<li>LG ThinQ controls your ductless heat pump anywhere with a Wi-Fi equipped device</li>\n 	<li>Energy-saving Inverter Compressor constantly adjusts to the right temperature</li>\n 	<li>Operates at low sound levels with LG’s unique skew fan and DUAL Inverter Compressor™\n- Stylish design that will fit in your room interior design and lighten your room.\n- Saves energy, perfect solution for additional heating source</li>\n</ul>\nAvailable in multiple BTUs.', 'LG Heat Pump', 'Low monthly payments', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '82-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-10-19 21:12:01', '2020-10-19 21:12:01', '', 82, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/82-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(648, 2, '2020-11-20 14:18:11', '2020-11-20 14:18:11', 'The <a href=\"http://google.com\" title=\"insert here\">Navien NCB-E</a> is the first high efficiency condensing combination boiler with the capacity to supply both heat and domestic hot water for larger homes — enough hydronic heat for a whole house, plus hot water to run two showers and a dishwasher all at the same time.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Takes up 80% less space than a traditional floor standing boiler and storage tank</li>\n 	<li>Wi-Fi enabled with NaviLink® add-on</li>\n 	<li>Built-in insulated buffer tank and recirculation pump to eliminate the \"cold water sandwich\" effect and issues of minimum flow rates commonly found in other tankless water heaters.</li>\n 	<li>Super condensing efficiency</li>\n 	<li>Dual stainless steel heat exchangers</li>\n</ul>\nAvailable in multiple BTUs', 'Navien Water Boiler', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '324-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-11-20 14:18:11', '2020-11-20 14:18:11', '', 324, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/324-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(649, 2, '2020-09-18 16:08:22', '2020-09-18 16:08:22', 'Improving your home’s efficiency doesn’t have to come at a high price. The Keeprite furnace is an affordable and efficient way to stay cozy and comfortable. With a reliable single-stage operation and fixed or 5-speed blower, you get even, consistent levels of temperature control. It also earns an up to 96% AFUE rating, which could be a significant increase in efficiency over your existing furnace.\n\n-Single-stage operation and fixed- or 5-speed speed blower motor options for even levels of temperature control and comfort\n- Dual fuel capable with a compatible heat pump and thermostat for energy-saving heating performance\n- Air purifier and humidifier compatible\n- High temperature limit control prevents overheating\n\nAvailable in multiple BTUs.', 'KeepRite Furnace', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '91-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-09-18 16:08:22', '2020-09-18 16:08:22', '', 91, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/91-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
