(651, 2, '2020-10-19 21:12:56', '2020-10-19 21:12:56', 'A trusted name in heating for over 100 years, Lennox offers the EL296E that heats at two different intensities, all in the name of striking the perfect balance of comfort and energy. It even enhances your comfort during the summertime – by operating a lower speed, it reduces moisture levels inside your home.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Two-stage variable speed helps find a balance between energy use and comfortable warmth</li>\n 	<li>196 AFUE uses 2/3 less energy than a standard motor – 96% efficiency\n-Saving energy means you save money on your monthly bills\n- High efficiency helps reduce your carbon footprint</li>\n</ul>\nAvailable in multiple BTUs', 'Lennox Furnace EL296E', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '311-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-10-19 21:12:56', '2020-10-19 21:12:56', '', 311, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/311-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(652, 2, '2020-10-19 21:12:29', '2020-10-19 21:12:29', 'Lennox Furnace heats at two different intensities to create the perfect balance of comfort and energy. In addition, it can adjust its airflow speed so it can gently spread an even level of heat throughout your home. It also prevents those uncomfortable blasts of air when you turn the system on.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Two-stage variable speed helps find a balance between energy use and comfortable warmth\n- 196 AFUE uses 2/3 less energy than a standard motor – 96% efficiency\n- Saving energy means you save money on your monthly bills</li>\n</ul>\nAvailable in multiple BTUs', 'Lennox Furnace', '<div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-start;\"><span class=\"price\"><sup>$</sup>0</span><span>&nbsp;Installation cost</span></div>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '77-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-10-19 21:12:29', '2020-10-19 21:12:29', '', 77, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/77-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(653, 2, '2020-09-18 16:44:07', '2020-09-18 16:44:07', '<ul>\n 	<li>High-efficiency solution</li>\n 	<li>Durable, weather-resistant</li>\n 	<li>Exceptional heat transfer</li>\n 	<li></li>\n 	<li>Available in multiple SEERs to better fit your home</li>\n</ul>', 'Lennox Air Conditioner', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '315-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-09-18 16:44:07', '2020-09-18 16:44:07', '', 315, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/315-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(654, 2, '2020-09-18 16:52:08', '2020-09-18 16:52:08', 'A Heat Recovery Ventilator RV (HRV) circulates air throughout a home, drawing in air from outside and expelling indoor air out. All air that moves through an HRV passes through a heat-exchange core, which regulates the temperature of the air that the HRV releases into the home and sends back outside.\n\nLifeBreath 155 Max Residential HRV\nMove air more efficiently through your home and lower your heating bills. The LifeBreath 155 Max features a High-Efficiency Hex Core to ensure maximum heat transfer, low-pressure loss, constructed of thermally conductive and durable aluminum.\n- Door Port Balancing &amp; adjustable dampers\n- Excellent low-temperature performance\n- Controller with 5-speed, 4-mode operation, included\n- Latched door to allow easy access to core and filters for cleaning. 25\" clearance recommended', 'HRV', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '321-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-09-18 16:52:08', '2020-09-18 16:52:08', '', 321, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/321-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(655, 2, '2020-09-18 16:53:40', '2020-09-18 16:53:40', 'Indoor pollution levels can be 25 times and occasionally 100 times more polluted than outdoor air, according to the EPA. A High-Efficiency Media or Electronic Air Cleaner is not enough to filter the millions of pollutants generated and infiltrating our homes daily. A HEPA Air Cleaner combined with an Electronic or Media Air Cleaner will provide much finer air filtration.\n- Ideal for allergy, asthma or respiratory sufferers\n- Reduces housekeeping time\n- Protects renovators and new home owners from excessive dust and odors off-gassed from new carpets, construction materials, paints, and more\n- Makes a noticeable difference for households with pets, offensive cooking odors and mustiness', 'HEPA Filtration', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '320-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-09-18 16:53:40', '2020-09-18 16:53:40', '', 320, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/320-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(656, 2, '2020-09-18 16:58:57', '2020-09-18 16:58:57', 'Saving energy doesn’t mean inconvenience. The Navien Tankless Water Heater has a built-in insulated buffer tank and recirculation pump to eliminate the \"cold water sandwich\" effect and issues of minimum flow rates commonly found in other tankless water heaters.\n- Dual stainless steel heat exchangers resist corrosion better than copper to provide longer life.\n- Wifi connectivity - Wi-Fi enabled with NaviLink® add-on\n- User-friendly control panel offers multiple features, including self-diagnostics', 'Navien Tankless Water Heater', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '322-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-09-18 16:58:57', '2020-09-18 16:58:57', '', 322, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/322-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(657, 2, '2020-09-18 17:03:09', '2020-09-18 17:03:09', 'Reverse osmosis systems offer one of the best ways of producing clean water for your household. Unlike other water filtering solutions, these systems are very efficient and capable of removing up to 95 to 99% of the contaminants in your water.\n\nExcalibur Superior Model 5 Stage Reverse Osmosis System\nEnjoy pure water drinking water the way nature intended it. With the Excalibur 5 Stage Reverse Osmosis system, you’ll enjoy pure refreshing water, crystal clear ice cubes and better tasting coffee, tea and fruit drinks.\n- 75 Gallons per day capacity\n- 5 micron Polypropylene spun filtration for silt, dirt, rust, turbidity and iron removal\n- 10 micron Carbon Block Filtration to eliminate chlorine, THM’s and taste and odour\n• 5 micron Carbon Block Filtration to remove volatile, industrial chemicals\n• Can be connected to refrigerator for water and ice', 'Reverse Osmosis', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '325-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-09-18 17:03:09', '2020-09-18 17:03:09', '', 325, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/325-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(658, 2, '2020-10-22 14:58:50', '2020-10-22 14:58:50', 'Hard water leaves your hair and skin scaly and dry. It also makes your clothes dingy and increases energy and water-heating costs. Water Softeners provide top-of-the-line protection against the many problems that hard water poses to a household.\n\nNovosoft 485HE Series Water Softener:\nUse up to 75% less salt and up to 64% less water with this premier high-efficiency softener. You’ll enjoy softer, better water, and it’s easier and faster to install than ever.\nReverse Flow Regeneration preserves an unused portion of softening bed from unnecessary exchange saving salt\nPrecision Brining calculates the exact amount of brine required to regenerate\nSoft Water Brine Tank Refill keeps tank &amp; injectors clean\nUser-friendly backlit LCD display', 'Water Softener', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '326-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-10-22 14:58:50', '2020-10-22 14:58:50', '', 326, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/326-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(659, 2, '2020-10-22 14:57:11', '2020-10-22 14:57:11', 'Rid your water of hardness &amp; bad tastes and odour caused by chlorine, chloramines, or organic matter. A full water treatment system gives you the best protection and best-tasting water.\n\nNovosoft 485 HTO:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Get fresher water – and keep it fresh. This unique two-tank system keeps the two media beds separate and allows for more carbon contact improving chlorine, chloramines, and organic removal. Plus, the two tanks make replacing key filters easier.</li>\n 	<li>Dedicated softening &amp; carbon filtration tanks provide truly refined water.</li>\n 	<li>NSF Certified control valve with electronic sensors, adjustable cycles &amp; proven piston, seal &amp; spacer design.</li>\n 	<li>Automatic system refresh flushes stagnant water.</li>\n 	<li>User-friendly backlit LCD display.</li>\n 	<li>48-hour self-charging battery back-up.</li>\n</ul>', 'Water Treatment System', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '327-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-10-22 14:57:11', '2020-10-22 14:57:11', '', 327, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/327-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
