s us well for the future. We look forward to commencing the tender process as soon as possible.”\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":500,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/08/24/2082594/0/en/Simply-Green-Home-Services-To-Make-Friendly-Premium-All-Cash-Offer-to-Acquire-Dealnet.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Completes $71 Million Acquisition of Home Capital Group’s Point-of-Sale Retail Lending Portfolio\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eThe sale is aligned with Home Capital’s strategy to exit non-core activities, while Simply Group looks to further fuel its growth in the consumer finance business by diversifying its product and consumer lending offerings beyond home energy solutions to home improvement generally.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":545,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20200903005822/en/\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"VersaBank Adds Simply Group Financial as Point-of-Sale Partner With Initial Financing of $72 Million\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e“We are thrilled to welcome Simply Group Financial as a new Point-of-Sale Financing partner,” said David Taylor, President and CEO, VersaBank. “It’s a great time to be joining forces with Simply Group Financial with the home improvement industry experiencing a boom as Canadians spend more of their discretionary income on home renovations and upgrades amidst the pandemic. VersaBank’s Point-of-Sale Financing business has been the primary driver of the significant expansion of our lending portfolio for the last eight years and we see this partnership as a tremendous opportunity for both organizations to execute on their growth strategies.”\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":500,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20200908005292/en/VersaBank-Adds-Simply-Group-Financial-Point-of-Sale-Partner\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Investors', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '156-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-14 12:41:52', '2020-10-14 12:41:52', '', 156, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/156-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
