=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022152\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2020\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-251\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-simply-retail-300x139.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022164\\u0022 height=\\u002276\\u0022 /\\u003e \\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-245\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-home-depot-300x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u002272\\u0022 height=\\u002272\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eLaunched Simply Green Retail Services with Home Depot.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eNamed Best Business of the Year (+100 employees) by the CanadianSME National Business Awards.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWe’re proud to have been ranked as Great Place To Work, 5 years in a row.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-240\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-CanadianSME-Award-300x125.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022209\\u0022 height=\\u002287\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-243\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022152\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green has been named Best Business of the Year (+100 employees)\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eThis honour was announced at an event hosted by CanadianSME Business Magazine in partnership with Cisco, Lenovo, and RBC, and is recognition of Simply Green’s rapid assent to the ranks of Canada’s most successful and leading companies.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":240,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 400px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-url\":\"/press-release/simply-green-has-been-named-best-business-of-the-year-100-employees/\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green recognized as one of the Best Workplaces™ in Canada\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e“Our employees have always been our biggest asset, so providing them with a positive, inclusive, fun and rewarding work environment is a priority for us. Each year, we strive to build a company culture that empowers and inspires performance. Our goal is to deliver the best possible employee experience, and, to make that happen, we are continuously looking for ways to raise the bar,” said Lawrence Krimker, CEO of Simply Group.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":243,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 250px;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"http://local-mysimplygreen/press_release/simply-green-recognized-as-one-of-the-best-workplaces-in-canada/\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Dealnet and Simply Group Acquisition Corp. Announce Successful Take-up of Shares under the Offer\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e“We would like to thank all of the Dealnet shareholders who have already taken advantage of this opportunity to realize the immediate value and tendered their shares. We are pleased to have taken up over 74% of Dealnet’s shares,” said Lawrence Krimker, CEO of The Simply Group.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":756,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/10/15/2109099/0/en/Dealnet-and-Simply-Group-Acquisition-Corp-Announce-Successful-Take-up-of-Shares-under-the-Offer.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Completes Acquisition of Snap Financial Group in a Transaction Valued at $511 Million\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0022SNAP Financial Group\'s strong portfolio and extensive dealer network unlocks immediate scale-efficiency and value for Simply Group, providing us with a distinct market advantage that we will leverage to deliver extraordinary growth in both assets under management and shareholder value,\\u0022 said \\u003cspan class=\\u0022xn-person\\u0022\\u003eLawrence Krimker\\u003c/span\\u003e, Founder and CEO of Simply Group.  \\u0022The combined strengths of Simply Group and SNAP will enable us to continue to drive innovation across a much-broader customer base with industry-changing products and services.\\u0022\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":740,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/10/15/2109099/0/en/Dealnet-and-Simply-Group-Acquisition-Corp-Announce-Successful-Take-up-of-Shares-under-the-Offer.html\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Completes $71 Million Acquisition of Home Capital Group’s Point-of-Sale Retail Lending Portfolio\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eThe sale is aligned with Home Capital’s strategy to exit non-core activities, while Simply Group looks to further fuel its growth in the consumer finance business by diversifying its product and consumer lending offerings beyond home energy solutions to home improvement generally.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":732,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/10/15/2109099/0/en/Dealnet-and-Simply-Group-Acquisition-Corp-Announce-Successful-Take-up-of-Shares-under-the-Offer.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"VersaBank Adds Simply Group Financial as Point-of-Sale Partner With Initial Financing of $72 Million\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e“We are thrilled to welcome Simply Group Financial as a new Point-of-Sale Financing partner,” said David Taylor, President and CEO, VersaBank. “It’s a great time to be joining forces with Simply Group Financial with the home improvement industry experiencing a boom as Canadians spend more of their discretionary income on home renovations and upgrades amidst the pandemic. VersaBank’s Point-of-Sale Financing business has been the primary driver of the significant expansion of our lending portfolio for the last eight years and we see this partnership as a tremendous opportunity for both organizations to execute on their growth strategies.”\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":735,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/simply-group-completes-acquisition-of-snap-financial-group-in-a-transaction-valued-at-511-million-885985213.html\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green Home Services To Make Friendly, Premium All-Cash Offer to Acquire Dealnet\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0022Simply Green has invested strategically to become a leader in the home comfort and home energy solutions sector, and this deal represents the next step in our continued growth. We are pleased this transaction will be adding over $200 million of finance receivables to our growing business,” said Lawrence Krimker, Chief Executive Officer of Simply Group. “With Simply Green’s expansive and growing product offerings, and Dealnet’s underlying strength, we believe this acquisition will benefit our customers and investors and positions us well for the future. We look forward to commencing the tender process as soon as possible.”\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":737,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/08/24/2082594/0/en/Simply-Green-Home-Services-To-Make-Friendly-Premium-All-Cash-Offer-to-Acquire-Dealnet.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Investors', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '156-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-23 16:38:42', '2020-10-23 16:38:42', '', 156, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/156-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
