(868, 8, '2020-12-07 00:05:28', '2020-12-07 00:05:28', '<!-- wp:block-lab/sg-hero {\"title\":\"We Answer Your Questions\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWhat do customers want to know most about us? Read on.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[]},\"image-side\":203,\"image-position\":\"bottom\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/faq-block {\"faqs\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"Who is Simply Green and how can they help?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eSimply Green helps Canadian homeowners upgrade their furnaces, air conditioners, water heaters, water filtration, and air filtration systems to provide healthier homes that use less energy.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"How do I know I should upgrade my furnace / AC?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eYour furnace, air conditioner, and water heating systems make up 50-75% of your home’s energy costs, so making them more efficient will help you save money and reduce your carbon footprint. Generally, equipment that is over 10-15-years-old signals a potential need to upgrade; however, a Simply Green technician can provide a detailed assessment of your equipment. As the technology has advanced, the government has upgraded the housing codes and some old equipment may be behind code and time for an upgrade.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"Why is leasing high-efficiency equipment better than buying?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eLeasing high-efficiency equipment (which includes a full maintenance program) is a great service for homeowners, because it:\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eSaves homeowners from large, upfront installation and equipment costs\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eProvides homeowners with expert technical service 24-7\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003eProvides homeowners low monthly payment options\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c/ul\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"Does leasing from Simply Green support my local businesses and community?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eOf course! Not only does Simply Green employ local sales and installation technicians, but we\'re always looking to expand our sales team with representatives from the local region. Along with that, a portion of our profits does go to local charities.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"What is ENERGY STAR® and why does it matter?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eENERGY STAR® is the international symbol of premium energy efficiency. Simply Green\'s top-of-the-line heating and cooling equipment carry ENERGY STAR® certifications. Look for the ENERGY STAR® label to save money on your energy bills and help protect our environment.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"What is Simply Green\'s relationship to Enbridge, Fortis BC, and other utilities?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eSimply Green Home Services is not owned by, or affiliated with, Enbridge Gas Distribution, or any other gas distributor. Nor is Simply Green affiliated with any government agency. Utilities such as Enbridge provide your home with natural gas, and do not offer equipment rentals. Simply Green has an \\u0022Open Bill Agreement\\u0022 with Enbridge Gas Distribution, which simply allows you to consolidate your rental fees with your gas expenses on one bill.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"What happens to my old equipment when I upgrade with Simply Green?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eIf your old equipment is leased, Simply Green will return it to your old provider, free of charge. If it\'s owned by you, we can dispose of it, free of charge, or leave it for you to keep (most people don\'t know how to dispose of equipment properly, so we don\'t mind doing it for you).\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"What forms of payment do you accept?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eLeasing payments are usually billed through Pre-Authorized Debit from any leading financial institution, unless in Ontario, where you can choose to have your payment consolidated with your Enbridge Gas Distribution bill. For purchases or buyouts, we accept cash, cheques, all major credit cards (VISA, MasterCard, American Express).\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"What should I do if I have a technical issue?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003ePlease give us a call at 1-800-764-5138 and speak with one of our client care representatives. We have a 24-hour emergency service line available for our clients.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"How can I refer a friend?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eOur clients are a constant source for new business, because they appreciate the quality of service we provide. Please give your friend our 1-800-764-5138 phone number or give us theirs and we\'ll have one of our reps contact them! We track our referral sources and will include you in our regular referral program bonuses (which change from time to time).\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"What if I want to stop my leasing program?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eGive us a call and we\'ll have one of our managers run you through your options. Cancelling the leasing program does remove the unlimited warranty, and free, 24-hour emergency service line.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"Is my personal information kept private?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eOf course! Please feel free to review our privacy policy.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"What happens to my leasing equipment if I move?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eIn the event that you move, give us a call and we can review your options and assist you in transferring the lease to the new homeowners.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"Help! I lost my sales agreement!\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eDon\'t worry! We keep copies of all agreements. If you need another copy, we can mail, email, or fax it to you, free of charge.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"question\":\"What does Simply Green\'s warranty cover?\",\"answer\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eSimply Green is proud to offer an extended warranty on all of its rental equipment, which covers all parts and labour for the duration of the lease. If we deem the equipment is past its useful life, we will replace it!\\u003c/p\\u003e\"}]},\"ctas\":{\"rows\":[]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/bottom-form {\"title\":\"Have a Question About Your Existing Products or Services?\",\"copy\":\"Are you an existing customer? We\'d be happy to help you with any questions you may have. Simply, fill out the form below and a member of our customer service team will get back to you shortly.\",\"include-both-forms\":true,\"new-form-title\":\"Looking for a New HVAC System?\",\"new-form-copy\":\"We have the right HVAC solution for you and experts that can help. Fill out the form below, and a member of our sales team will get back to you shortly.\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '165-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-12-07 00:05:28', '2020-12-07 00:05:28', '', 165, 'https://www.mysimplygreen.com/165-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(871, 2, '2020-12-08 16:44:28', '2020-12-08 16:44:28', '<!-- wp:block-lab/sg-hero {\"title\":\"We\'re Simply Green\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWe’re in the business of making you and your family more comfortable.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"http://local-mysimplygreen/contact-us#contact-form\",\"link-text\":\"We\'re here to help\",\"link-style\":\"button\"},{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Call Us\",\"link-url\":\"tel:18007645138\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]},\"image-side\":196,\"image-position\":\"center\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Best in the Business\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eOur goal is to make your home more energy-efficient and environmentally friendly.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWe were founded on the simple premise of improving your overall comfort and quality of life. You’ve got access to the best and brightest minds in the HVAC industry. Our technical and service professionals are all certified, licensed, and provide unparalleled service and support. They can handle any job – big or small.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":198,\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Happy Employees Happy Results\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWe could tell you that Simply Green employees love the work they do for our customers, but the fact that they’ve voted us as a Great Place to Work® – for the sixth consecutive year – speaks for itself! This country-wide certification – conducted independently by Great Place to Work® Institute Canada – is based on direct, thorough and anonymous feedback from employees about their workplace experience. We’ve come a long way as a Great Place to Work.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":197,\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"/careers/\",\"link-text\":\"Learn More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"},{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Call Us\",\"link-url\":\"tel:18007645138\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed'