48\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eAcquired \\u003ca href=\\u0022https://www.sandpiperenergysolutions.ca/\\u0022\\u003eSandpiper Energy Solutions\\u003c/a\\u003e from Oakville Hydro (“OEC”) with 24,000 clients.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eAwarded Top 25 Great Places to Work.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eDwight Duncan and Geoffrey Belsher added to the Board of Directors.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-243\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022151\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2017\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-824\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Green_planet_logo.jpg\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022260\\u0022 height=\\u002259\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eAcquired Green Planet Home Services (“GP”) with 1,700 accounts, Ontario Consumers Home Services (“OCHS”) and Simply Comfort Home Services (“SCHS”) with ~53,000 accounts.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2018\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eAwarded Top 15 Great Places to Work.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-243\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022152\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2019\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eAwarded Top 4 Great Places to Work.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-243\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022152\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"},{\"\":\"\",\"year\":\"2020\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-251\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-simply-retail-300x139.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022164\\u0022 height=\\u002276\\u0022 /\\u003e \\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-245\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-home-depot-300x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u002272\\u0022 height=\\u002272\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eLaunched Simply Green Retail Services with Home Depot.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eNamed Best Business of the Year (+100 employees) by the CanadianSME National Business Awards.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWe’re proud to have been ranked as Great Place To Work, 5 years in a row.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-240\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-CanadianSME-Award-300x125.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022209\\u0022 height=\\u002287\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cimg class=\\u0022alignnone  wp-image-243\\u0022 src=\\u0022http://local-mysimplygreen/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logo-GPTW-297x300.png\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022 width=\\u0022150\\u0022 height=\\u0022152\\u0022 /\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green has been named Best Business of the Year (+100 employees)\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eThis honour was announced at an event hosted by CanadianSME Business Magazine in partnership with Cisco, Lenovo, and RBC, and is recognition of Simply Green’s rapid assent to the ranks of Canada’s most successful and leading companies.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":1011,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 400px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-style\":\"button\",\"link-url\":\"/press-release/simply-green-has-been-named-best-business-of-the-year-100-employees/\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Green recognized as one of the Best Workplaces™ in Canada\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e“Our employees have always been our biggest asset, so providing them with a positive, inclusive, fun and rewarding work environment is a priority for us. Each year, we strive to build a company culture that empowers and inspires performance. Our goal is to deliver the best possible employee experience, and, to make that happen, we are continuously looking for ways to raise the bar,” said Lawrence Krimker, CEO of Simply Group.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":243,\"no-dot\":\"no-dot\",\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: 250px;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-url\":\"http://local-mysimplygreen/press_release/simply-green-recognized-as-one-of-the-best-workplaces-in-canada/\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Completes Acquisition of Dealnet in Transaction Valued at over $243 Million\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e\\u0022The Dealnet acquisition is highly strategic, and complementary to our business.  With Dealnet on board we have further cemented our competitive advantage in the home improvement financing space.  Our unprecedented dealer network will have access to a best-in-class suite of financing products and a significantly improved digital application experience,\\u0022 said \\u003cspan class=\\u0022xn-person\\u0022\\u003eLawrence Krimker\\u003c/span\\u003e, Founder and CEO of Simply Group.  \\u0022No other Canadian home financing company can offer comparable opportunities to its dealers.  We will continually look for new ways to enhance our dealer programs and bolster the value we offer them.\\u0022\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":849,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/simply-group-completes-acquisition-of-dealnet-in-transaction-valued-at-over-243-million-808176167.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Simply Group Acquisition Corp. Acquires 93.13% of Dealnet Capital Corp. and Commences Compulsory Acquisition\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e“With the acquisition of Dealnet well on its way towards successful completion, I would like to thank Dealnet’s valued shareholders, employees and partners for their overwhelming support,” said Brent Houlden, Dealnet Chief Executive Officer. “We’re delighted that our strategic review process resulted in a premium offer for shareholders and believe that we have found an ideal owner for the business in Simply Group and industry veteran Lawrence Krimker.”\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":808,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: center center;\\nbackground-size: cover;\\nmargin-bottom:40px;\",\"link-list\":{\"rows\":[{\"\":\"\",\"link-url\":\"https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/simply-group-completes-acquisition-of-dealnet-in-transaction-valued-at-over-243-million-808176167.html\",\"link-text\":\"Read More\",\"link-style\":\"button\"}]}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:block-lab/half-and-half {\"title\":\"Dealnet and Simply Group Acquisition Corp. Announce Successful Take-up of Shares under the Offer\",\"copy\":\"\\u003cp\\u003e“We would like to thank all of the Dealnet shareholders who have already taken advantage of this opportunity to realize the immediate value and tendered their shares. We are pleased to have taken up over 74% of Dealnet’s shares,” said Lawrence Krimker, CEO of The Simply Group.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"image\":756,\"background-styles\":\"background-repeat: no-repeat;\\nbackground-position: cen